00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Think of the plane as a rubber grid; arrows are the unit directions.

2
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:16.000
A matrix A warps everything together: it pushes, stretches, and shears.

3
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Area scales by det(A). The unit square becomes a parallelogram of area det(A).

